<br>
Concussion was said to be level 39 because it helps regaining concentration when you cast a spell at least 10 levels below your current level, not because of fizzles. This is obviously important for a spell like concussion, which is meant to be cast when you're being beaten on.<br>
<br>
Root cannot/will not be strengthened because it might make tanking redundant at some levels. Why bother having tanks if you can just root mobs reliably out of melee range and nuke/dot/shoot them to bits?<br>
<br>
The Skyfire port is hardly suicidal. I've used it many times, only been aggroed about 3 of those times, and never even came close to dying. <p>Darth Eldritch<BR>
